articles.description: It will also be a crowning moment for City, who despite all their successes in Premier League, are still looking for their first European trophy since 2008. | Football News
articles.content: The 2022-23 European football season will come to an end with a marquee matchup in the UEFA Champions League final, being contested between English and Italian giants Manchester City and Inter Milan.… [+2601 chars]
